eclipse:
eclipse添加动态库：
		//在Debug下的objects.mk，中添加：LIBS :=-lpthread
		Properties->C/C++ Build->Settings->Tool Settings->Cross G++ Linker->
		Libraries->Libraries(-l)->添加pthread
libdvbpsi环境：
		examples/.libs/decode_pmt	并在Environment中添加
		LD_LIBRARY_PATH - /home/barmaco/libdvbpsi-1.2.0/src/.libs



